qxi1665703179816.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qxi1665703179816.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qxi1665703179816.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qxi1665703179816\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Encode raw data in Base64 format\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__topic_d132692e1_d132693e1_d132694e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__p_d132695e1_d132696e1_d132697e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">extern long URawToB64(const unsigned char *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">In</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, long</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Inlen</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, unsigned char *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, long</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutMaxLen</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">);</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__section_w4383ab1b5b3_w4384ab1b5_w4385ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194905e83\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Direction</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">In</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Data that is to be encoded</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InLen</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Length of the data that is to be encoded</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">OUT</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Base64 encoded result</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutMaxLen</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15824e1_d15825e1_d15826e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Maximum number of bytes that can be written to <var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__section_w4386ab1b5b5_w4387ab1b5_w4388ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194905e227\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\">&lt; 0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\">Not all characters have been\n                    encoded.<p class=\"p\">(<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> x <var class=\"keyword varname\">ReturnValue</var>) have been\n                  encoded.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\"> 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\">Failed to encode in base64</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\">&gt; 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qxi1665703179816__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\">All characters have been encoded. The value is the\n                actual length of the output data.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__section_w4389ab1b5b7_w4390ab1b5_w4391ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194905e294\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__p_d132800e1_d132801e1_d132802e1\">Library <span class=\"ph filepath\">uenc</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__section_w4392ab1b5b9_w4393ab1b5_w4394ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194905e305\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qxi1665703179816__p_d132647e1_d132648e1_d132649e1\">This function is useful for creating security drivers\n        that need to encode and decode data.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bff1665703179971.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UB64ToRaw</a><p>Decode a null terminated Base64 encoded string to raw data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531465\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531465\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "URawToB64 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Encode raw data in Base64 format extern long URawToB64(const unsigned char * In , long Inlen , unsigned char * Out , long OutMaxLen ); Parameters Parameter Direction Description In IN Data that is to be encoded InLen IN Length of the data that is to be encoded Out OUT Base64 encoded result OutMaxLen IN Maximum number of bytes that can be written to Out Return Values Value Meaning < 0 Not all characters have been encoded. ( -1 x ReturnValue ) have been encoded. 0 Failed to encode in base64 > 0 All characters have been encoded. The value is the actual length of the output data. Use Library uenc Description This function is useful for creating security drivers that need to encode and decode data. Related Links UB64ToRaw Decode a null terminated Base64 encoded string to raw data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}